parameters:
\n< Foreman >Yo, how was it today? Spread your ass wide,
okay?
\n< Foreman >This is going to become quite the rumor.

\n< Serena >I don't care. But more importantly,
remember our promise.

\n< Foreman >Madam sure is peculiar, huh? Doing things
like purposely letting a caged bird
escape...

\n< Serena >I won't run away. I will definitely repay
the borrowed money.
\n< Serena >That's exactly why I'm going to the guild.
\n< Foreman >...Hey hey, now? After dancing all night?

\n< Serena >No problem. But time is precious, so let's
not waste it.

\n< Foreman >...Well, I won't stop you. The door is unlocked.
Just go out as it is.

\n< Foreman >You understand, right? Night is also a time
for work.
\n< Serena >...No problem.
\n< Foreman >It's enviable to be young, huh?
\n< Serena >Mmm...

\n< Serena >Sigh... I can't believe how I ended up in this
situation...
\n< Serena >But today is the promised deadline.

\n< Serena >The informant should report some clues
about Splendore...

\n< Serena >For that, I paid 250G... 25,000S. I even
borrowed 5,000S as a debt.

\n< Serena >Thanks to all the hardships... today,
everything will be rewarded. Let's go to
the guild and meet up with the
informant.
\n< Serena >It's the building just south of here.

events.name: 第二部ストーリー　シシリア

parameters: ストーリー　シシリア

\n< Deacon >Hey, your dance moves are really impressive
today. I was surprised when I heard you
were going out all night.

\n< Deacon >With that big belly of yours, it's quite
impressive how you can dance so
gracefully.

\n< Deacon >The customers are constantly interested in
you. I can understand why Madam likes
you a little bit.

\n< Serena >I can't say that I'm behaving so freely
though...

\n< Serena >It was probably convenient for you that I
didn't show my face all day. You were
probably teasing and raising the
price... most likely.
\n< Deacon >Madam is really sweet on you, huh?

\n< Serena >You must have calculated everything. It was
convenient for you that I didn't show my
face all day. Teasing and raising the
price... most likely.
\n< Deacon >Hehe, yeah, that might be true.

\n< Deacon >Alright, then that's the end of your dancing.
From the next hour, please entertain the
customers.
\n< Serena >Okay. I'll go right away.

\n< Deacon >Oh? You're not complaining? You usually
have a face like you stepped on shit.
\n< Serena >I'm desperate too.

\n< Deacon >Oh, did getting kicked in the ass by Madam
motivate you? Quite impressive, quite
impressive...

\n< Deacon >Well then, I'll have you go upstairs with
the next customer for entertainment. Do
you understand what I mean?
\n< Serena >.......

\n< Deacon >Madam says not to worry because the customer
won't do anything reckless.
\n< Serena >...To say don't worry...

\n< Serena >......I understand. I can't refuse
anyway.......

\n< Deacon >Hehe. Good, you've got a nice expression.
You've given up and learned to flatter,
that's the face of a decent prostitute.
